timelineItems.text: Sure it was a nice strike but Giovinco had time to make a ham sandwich before he shot. #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Gary Bourque
timelineItems.text: just over 12min in and Gio causing all kinds of problems for portland #tfclive

timelineItems.name: Dan Brunell
timelineItems.text: It's amazing how much bigger the midfield of Toronto is compared to Portland. Knocking us off the ball and winning headers. #RCTID

timelineItems.title: HIGHLIGHTS: Toronto FC vs. Portland Timbers | May 23, 2015
